## Camera easing

```js
function updateCamera() {
  camera.x += (target.x - camera.x) * config.theta;
  camera.y += (target.y - camera.y) * config.theta;
  camera.zoom += (target.zoom - camera.zoom) * config.theta;
}
```

Simple interpolation.

